Comment: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:53.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP Start
Comment: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,大切な落とし物を
Comment: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,知らない君が拾って
Comment: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,届けてくれたみたいな
Comment: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,思いがけない朝
Comment: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:19.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そういえば大事なものは
Comment: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ちゃんと名前を書かなくじゃ
Comment: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,どこかで失くしてしまうと
Comment: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,よく言われてたのに
Comment: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:30.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　せいじゃなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　ものでもなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,変わらず　世界は
Comment: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そこにあるよ
Comment: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,風と　さあ手と手繋いで
Comment: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,空と　息を合わせて
Comment: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,行こう　動き出した
Comment: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,心の矢印
Comment: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,君と　そう君とならば
Comment: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:56.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ならば　そう君とだから
Comment: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:04.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,何が起きるかなんかわからない未来が
Comment: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,走る
Comment: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.90,OPJP,last,0,0,0,karaoke,キラキラ　跳ねてる
Comment: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP End
Comment: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:53.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍贵的失物
Comment: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相识的你捡起
Comment: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:13.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交还给我
Comment: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:19.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这么说来　重要的东西
Comment: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要写上名字
Comment: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然会丢失于不知何处
Comment: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,经常被这样告诫
Comment: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:30.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的错
Comment: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不属于任何人
Comment: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一成不变的世界
Comment: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,存在于此
Comment: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,随风　来吧手牵手
Comment: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,于空　配合对方步调
Comment: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出发了
Comment: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:50.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,与你　没错　如果与你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:56.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,没错　正因为与你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:04.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,向着未知的未来
Comment: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,奔跑
Comment: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.90,OPCN,last,0,0,0,karaoke,闪耀夺目
